{"tid":2183958,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何謂三權不再分立？","createTime":"2020-09-01T09:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T10:08:03.000Z","uid":116547,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4f9def5b0ad3dcdcc0e099cd856841c3c285e8a6","tid":2183958,"uid":116547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:02:23.000Z","msg":"見好多人一直斟酌係香港不嬲都有三權分立 brabrabra...<br />\n但我想講呢個位根本吾係重點，而係佢集權想做乜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nJBDhfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnJBDhfe.jpg&h=5aa1c88b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將所有權力集中係行政長官身上，係對行政，立法，司法機關有較大同直接控制權。<br />\n會唔會係想立法繞過立法會？<br />\n係審訊有關國家安全既犯人時，安排法官有更大便利？<br />\n甚至直接派軍隊入城？<br />\n<br />\n大概呢啲先係我地要留意"},{"pid":"1eff54dbf3d51d4a33a5ba49f8d59443d3dd104d","tid":2183958,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:14:14.000Z","msg":"繞過立法會立法係遲早既事，你咪睇下到時真係35+會點<br />\n<br />\n到時實會分立法性質分開，某d法俾果堆所謂議員立，某d法就政府立，至於咩法掟入立會咩法係政府立，就由政府話事。"},{"pid":"d4d328b204a8c14818fe61390ffd94ba4be7296c","tid":2183958,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:16:12.000Z","msg":"獨裁專制"},{"pid":"ac5237355a9c9aec7ce64c929929abc0c8a15461","tid":2183958,"uid":116547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:36:27.000Z","msg":"集權就係獨裁第一步"},{"pid":"16cd44da0ade3fe44d8c4594d4533afb86715d14","tid":2183958,"uid":229508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:37:10.000Z","msg":"黨大於一切"},{"pid":"16f38e9c5478917f146e2e928c693d34eb566961","tid":2183958,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702fb1f1151ddf2622f489b52fc10a70760a3370","tid":2183958,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":